OL,6,FThe mother of a young woman - whose
OL,7,Fdaughter's drug addiction led her into
OL,8,Fsex work - has described the man who
OL,9,Ftrafficked her as a "monster".
OL,11,FDeborah Hanna spoke out as that man
OL,12,Ffaces sentencing for a number of
OL,13,Fserious sex and drug crimes, not only
OL,14,Fagainst her daughter but other young
OL,15,Fwomen.
OL,17,FDerek Brown, aged 61 who is originally
OL,18,Ffrom Lisburn, is currently behind bars
OL,19,Fin Lisburn.
