OL,6,F"I had no clue whatsoever that all
OL,7,Fthis was going on, and that was my own
OL,8,Fdaughter, so if I didn't know that,
OL,9,Fthen I'm sure a lot of people out
OL,10,Fthere don't know," she said.
OL,12,F"I often sit and think about the
OL,13,Fvulnerable situations she would have
OL,14,Fbeen in, like going to them
OL,15,Fappointments and who she was meeting.
OL,16,FThat could have been anybody. To think
OL,17,Fshe was being put in them situations
OL,18,Fjust terrifies me."
OL,20,FThere's not a day Deborah doesn't
OL,21,Fthink about her eldest.
